pmath is a python library.
pmath was developed to use advanced mathematical functions.
pmath makes it easy to calculate complex numbers.
Try to expand the world of mathematics with pmath.
The function of pmath can be seen for each version in the upper right.
The current version of pmath is v.0.0.1.
